Dialogs.Dialog: Hey.
Nene
What is it？
Umm, about a kiss...
Eh！？ Ah, yes！？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, do you actually... hate to kiss？
Eh...？ Why？
Somehow, you always seem very nervous when we kiss...
...Is that so？
Yeah... So I think that you might hate it.
That's not the case！ It's... It's a little...
A little？
It's... a little... Well... Just a little embarrassing...
I-Is that so...？
Hey.
Nene
What is it？
I just want to hear your opinion. What do you think about... a kiss？
What do I think...？ I like it.
R-Really？
Hehe, really. But rather than like, it makes me feel relieved.
I see.
What's the matter？
I was thinking that you might hate it but just tried to bear with it.
Really？ ...If that's the case, what would you do？
What would I do？ I...
I'll tell you one thing.
It feels really good when you kiss me. It really makes me happy, okay？
I see... Somehow, this is embarrassing.
Hehe. Hehehe. Your face now is very cute▼
(I'm no match for her...)
Hey.
Nene
What is it？
It might be sudden, but... What do you think about my kiss？
？*What do I think？ Are you worried about it？
I wonder if you might hate it...
What？ Why？ I don't hate it.
Okay. I probably think too much.
Yeah, you think too much. Anyway, the mood and the timing are very important, and you must not rush it, okay？
Urgh, I'll try my best.
Yeah. This big sister will be rooting for you▼
(R-Rooting for me...！？)
Hey.
Nene
What is it？
About a kiss...
Eh？ Ah, yeah. What？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. What do you think about it？
Well... Hmm... Can I tell you frankly？
Y-Yeah...
I still don't know about something like that...
...Sorry for asking such a weird question.
Don't worry. I'm sorry that I can't give you a proper answer.
(This is getting awkward.)
Nene
Hey, you got a minute？
Yeah, what is it？
Well... Hey, when we kissed...
Eh？
Ah, no. I wonder what you were thinking when we kissed...
...I wasn't thinking about anything.
You weren't thinking about anything？
I mean I didn't feel calm enough to be thinking about anything else...
...I see.
But... I could feel it.
Eh！？ You mean our lips... or something like that？
That, too... But I could feel your love. I could tell that you love me.
I see...
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, how about you？
Me！？ Ah, well... Same, I think. Yeah, it's the same... I think.
Nene
Hey, you got a minute？
Yeah, what is it？
This might be a little difficult to answer, but... Do you like it when we kiss？
Well...
Hmm... If you don't like it, we don't have to kiss.
That's...
Because you always take your time until you kiss me, right？ So...
No. I kiss you because I really want to.
Really...？
I don't hate it. But if I do it recklessly, I'm afraid that you might not like it...
Then that's the reason why you're nervous.
Yeah... I can't decide if I should kiss you or not.
I see... Hehe. So, that's why.
Sorry to make you worry about this.
No. If that's what concerns you, just try to choose the right timing, okay？
O-Okay... I'll try.
Hehe. So cute▼
Nene
Hey, you got a minute？
Yeah, what is it？
Hey, do you like it when we kiss？
I'm worried. Please. Can you answer me？
...I like it.
Why do you like it？
W-Why...？
I can tell you, all right？
Really？
Yeah. I like it when we kiss. I love it.
W-Why？
Hehe. When you can answer my previous question clearly, I'll tell you.
Eh！？
Until you find the answer, we shall keep kissing. But, remember. It's not something you can do anytime, anywhere, okay？
(I wonder... whether she's teasing me now.)
Hey.
Nene
What is it？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, do you remember when you confessed to me？
Yeah, I remember... Why？
Were you scared？
I was scared... But, I'd feel more scared if I didn't get it out.
Really？
Because... If I kept quiet and someone else confessed to you before I did...
If that happened, I probably wouldn't be able to forgive myself.
That's why I made up my mind to confess to you. If you rejected me, that would be fine.
I see... But I didn't reject you, okay？
Yeah, you accepted my feelings. I was very happy.
I was the one who was happy...
Ah... Hehe, okay.
Hey.
Nene
What is it？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, were you nervous when you confessed to me？
Eh！？ W-Why do you ask all of a sudden！？
Well, I just want to know.
Umm... Well. I wasn't nervous... I think.
Really！？
It's more like I was in a panic.
It was like my heart was about to explode and it was difficult to breathe. I looked calm but I wasn't calm at all...
So, it wasn't nervousness. It was something much worse, okay？
I see...
Are you satisfied now？
Yeah. If I didn't ask you, I wouldn't know this.
Hehe. Then you should be prepared that I might ask you some sudden questions later too, okay？
Hey.
Nene
What is it？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, what were you thinking when you confessed to me？
Eh？ What do you mean？
To confess to someone, you really need a lot of courage, right？
Hehe. It's not courage, you know？
Really？
Yeah. I... actually just wanted to end my anxiety. So I made up my mind.
I had to study, to work, and to do a lot of things. But no matter what, I couldn't stop thinking about you. That was bad.
So... You decided to confess？
Yeah. I was really scared, but it would be worse if I didn't...
It was like an adventure for me somehow.
And... I knew I dared to do that because the one I fell in love with was you...
It's like I'm confessing to you again now. Hehe.
Hey.
Nene
What is it？
What if I want to confess to ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲...？
Eh？ ...Eeeeeeh！？
Just a what-if. Only a what-if situation.
Ah, a what-if...？ I see... Yeah, right...
No, never mind. So, if you want to confess to me？
Yeah. If I want to confess to ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, what should I do？
Hmm... So, it's from my point of view, right？
Yeah. What kind of confession would ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ want to hear？
If it's me... I'd like to hear a straightforward confession. Just get it out.
I see... Yeah, it's better to just get it out.
...Yes.
What's the matter？
Eh？ Ah, no. It's nothing. Yeah, it's really nothing.
Hey.
Nene
What is it？
What do you think we will be like from now on？
Eh？ What do you mean？
Somehow, I'm just worrying about our future...
I've never thought about it, but...
Yeah, now I wonder how we will be. Will we break up sometime later？
Hmm... But I can't think about dating anyone else except you.
Yeah. Same.
Then it's fine like this, right？
Like this？
You don't have to worry about it.
...Yeah, you're right.
Yeah. I love you, okay？ I'll always love you.
Hey.
Nene
What is it？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, do you regret it that you confessed to me？
Eh！？
...Am I a good boyfriend？ I wonder.
Ah... Are you worried because I'm older than you？
I'm not sure... I really don't know why I'm worried.
I'm also worried and I wish that I could be younger than you.
Is that so...？
Even though you're younger than me, it's not like you're not reliable.
So... Yeah, even though I still care how people would see us, that's just something trivial.
But, even if you're okay with it...
You should have more confidence in yourself. You're the person I love, okay？
...Yeah, you're right. Sorry for being weird.
Hehe. Pull yourself together, my boyfriend▼
Hey.
Nene
What is it？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, do you enjoy going out with me？
Eh！？ What is this all of a sudden？
Hmm... I'm younger than ,you, so you might think that I'm childish...
...Yeah, you're actually a little childish, I think.
As I thought...
Yeah, I feel like you're childish to ask me such a question.
I love you. That's why I confessed to you. Got it？
...Yes.
You're like this, and that's why I love you, okay？ The childish part, and the other parts, I love everything in you.
...Okay.
So don't worry, okay？ When you want to act spoiled, I'll let you. All right？
(▲姉ヶ崎＊▲... You really are more mature than me.)
Hey.
Nene
What is it？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, do you think you easily get jealous？
I'm not sure. What do you think？
Hmm... I can't imagine you getting jealous.
Okay. Then I'm not jealous.
I can trust you, right？ That's why I don't get jealous.
But I'm a little sad that you wouldn't get jealous for me.
Then should I... get jealous？
Maybe you should.
Then maybe I will. But... don't intentionally try to make me get jealous, okay？
Hey.
Nene
What is it？
If I get close to other girls, will you be jealous？
Get close... How close？
For example... As close as ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ and me.
I won't get jealous.
Really！？
If you're that close, you must be dating her, right？ That means you already dumped me. I wouldn't have the right to be jealous.
Sorry for asking something weird.
No, I'm also sorry for giving you such a weird answer.
Are we good now？
Yup, we're good.
Hey.
Nene
What is it？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, you don't easily get jealous, right？
Hehe. Do you want me to be jealous？
No, I don't.
You'll never betray me, right？
Of course I won't.
Then even if you get close to other girls, I won't be jealous.
Hmm... But maybe you should get jealous a little bit...
A boyfriend's request？ Hehe. Then I'll be jealous whenever you talk to or look at other girls, okay？
But that's not what I want...
Geez. I'll be jealous occasionally then. Are you satisfied now？
...You don't have to. Sorry for asking such a weird question.
Don't worry. To think that you wanted me to do something like this, I'm a little happy.
Hey.
Nene
What is it？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. Do you think you usually get jealous？
Wow... What a serious question.
Sorry for asking something weird. I'm just curious.
Well... I can get very jealous.
Very？ Like, getting violent？
No. I'd be very quiet and brood over it. My jealousy would pile up then.
You jealousy would pile up...？
If my boyfriend betrayed me, I'm probably done for.
...Done for？
(Her eyes... Her eyes are scary...)
...That's what I think. I've never experienced it myself, so I still don't understand that feeling.
...I see. I'm relieved...
Hehe. But I wonder how it would feel. I'm not sure if I want to know it or not. It can be scary...
(Yeah...)
Hey.
Nene
What is it？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, what are you like when you get jealous？
Eh？ What...？ I think we've talked about this before... Hmm.
You don't know？
Yeah, I can't picture it. Maybe I don't get jealous...
Then suppose that you get jealous...？
Hmm... I think I'll be crying first.
Crying？
There has to be the reason that makes me get jealous, right？
Yeah, right...
Do you want to make me cry？
No way.
Hehe. I'll trust you with your words, okay？
Hey.
Nene
What is it？
Well, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, what will you be like when you get jealous？
We talked about this before, right？ What will I be like...？ I think I can stay calm...
What if I talk to a girl you don't know？
...Umm, that's fine.
What if I have dinner with her？
I'd probably get a little irritated... Ah, but I'd have my special measurement in the case.
Special measurement？
If you do something that you should only do to me to that girl, I'll get jealous.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, what do you mean by "something I should only do to you"？
There are a lot of things, right？
Hmm... Sorry, I really don't know.
Hehe. It's okay that I'm the only one who knows what they are.
Hey.
Nene
What is it？
Just for example, if I make you jealous, what will you be like, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲？
Why do you ask me that question？
I'm just curious.
With that question, you make me doubt whether you've cheated on me.
I didn't do anything.
Really？
Really.
If it's just a little bit, I can try to overlook it.
I didn't do anything. Really, it's nothing.
Hehe. Then you didn't have to ask me that question.
(Hmm, did she try to avoid answering it？)
Hey.
Nene
What is it？
Tell me the truth. ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, do you like skinship？
Eh？ ...What is this all of a sudden？
Ah, well, I'm afraid that I'm clinging to you too much and that might not be good.
Could it be that... I make you feel bad？
No, that's not the case.
That's good to hear... Well...
Even now, I'm still a little nervous. ...And that's the reason. It's not because I hate it.
Plus... If you made me feel uncomfortable, I'd tell you honestly...
Which means... sometimes I cling to you too much？
Just a little bit. Ah, but I still want you to be close to me, no matter what...
Then let's try to progress a little bit at a time...
Yeah... That's right. A little bit at a time...
Hey.
Nene
What is it？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. Do you like skinship？
Come on. There are people who don't like others to cling onto them too much.
Is... that so？ I think it's rare to find anyone like that.
Really？
Maybe I don't know that many people. What do you think then？
Me？ For me, if it's with ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, I think I like it.
Then we're not gonna do it. Skinship will be forbidden for a while.
Eh！？
Just kidding！
W-What？
Hehe. Hehehe. So cute▼
Hey.
Nene
What is it？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, what do you think about people who are clinging to you？
Skinship, you mean？ I don't hate it. Why？
But you don't like it when the guy is being too assertive, right？
Ah... Hmm.
W-What？
So, you mean you're the assertive type, huh？
No, I didn't mean that...
Girls are vulnerable, so you have to be gentle and handle them with care, all right？
...I'll be careful.
Hehe. But if you can read the mood well, this big sister is very generous, you know？
...What do you mean？
The mood is very important. I'm also a girl... okay？
Hey.
Nene
What is it？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲. What do you think about skinship？
Eh？ Why do you ask all of a sudden？
Somehow, I'm just curious about it. Well, people have different opinions, right？
For me... It depends on my partner, I think.
I see. For example, if you're dating a guy, it'd be okay if he touches you, right？
Yeah, that's right. It's all up to him.
I see. I think I get it.
Hehe. You're so caring.
Hey.
Nene
What is it？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, what do you think about my skinship？
I don't hate it... Hmm, I think I like it more than before.
I see. I wonder if it's okay that I always do it...
What？ Do you mean you actually hate it？
That's not what I meant.
Hehe. Well, there are times when I feel very happy that you touch me.
Really？
Yeah, I'm very happy. But there are times when I feel embarrassed, too.
I see...
Hey.
Nene
What is it？
People say that skinship is important for lovers... ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, what do you think？
I think it's very important, but... What's the matter？
Well... I've been wondering what kind of skinship you'd like.
For example？
For example... Well...
If I grab your hand like this？
Yeah...
Or... Should I get closer to you？
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲... That's too close.
What about when I pat your head, or when I tickle your ears, or when I pinch your cheeks？
W-Wait.
Hehehe.
Y-You scared me...
It's really fun to tease you▼
(Urgh, she was just toying with me...)
Hey.
Nene
What is it？
People say that skinship is important for lovers... ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, what do you think？
Eh？ What's the matter？
About my skinship... I wonder what you think.
I really love it.
I-Is that so...？
When you touch me, or caress me, or whisper something in my ears, or hug me...
Actually, I feel very happy just by hearing your voice.
I know it's bad, but I think it's too late to do anything with it.
Too late？
I'm already addicted to my boyfriend. I feel uneasy when you're not around, and I feel very happy when you're with me.
Then I think I'm also addicted to my girlfriend.
Geez... You've said something nice.
